style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">FDA approved =
Casgevy</a><span>, a CRISPR-based therapy for sickle cell anemia, but this =
new approach would allow patients to simply take a pill. Given these molecu=
lar glue degraders were just discovered, we&#8217;re likely at least a few =
years out from commercialization as potential new therapeutics go through t=
rials and approval phases, but the discovery is an important step in develo=
ping a universally effective and accessible treatment for SCD.</span></p><p=
